-                    "content": "---\npgg:\n  topic: \"dashboard-board-polish-and-i18n-fix\"\n  stage: \"plan\"\n  status: \"reviewed\"\n  skill: \"pgg-plan\"\n  score: 95\n  updated_at: \"2026-04-23T04:04:53Z\"\nreactflow:\n  node_id: \"spec-i18n\"\n  node_type: \"doc\"\n  label: \"spec/i18n/dashboard-locale-coverage.md\"\nstate:\n  summary: \"dashboard locale coverageмҷҖ hard-coded copy м ңкұ° кё°мӨҖмқ„ м •мқҳн•ңлӢӨ.\"\n  next: \"task.md мҠ№мқё\"\n---\n\n# Dashboard Locale Coverage Spec\n\n## Goal\n\n- dashboardм—җм„ң л¶Җл¶„ м Ғмҡ© мғҒнғңлЎң лӮЁм•„ мһҲлҠ” locale мІҙкі„лҘј shell, board, detail/history, settings, derived labelк№Ңм§Җ мқјкҙҖлҗҳкІҢ нҷ•мһҘн•ңлӢӨ.\n\n## Locale-First Rules\n\n- мғҲ UI copyлҠ” inline stringмңјлЎң л„Јм§Җ м•ҠлҠ”лӢӨ.\n- кё°мЎҙ hard-coded helper, badge, status label, metric label, empty/error copyлҸ„ locale dictionaryлЎң мҲҳл ҙмӢңнӮЁлӢӨ.\n- `ko/en` parityлҘј мң м§Җн•ңлӢӨ.\n\n## Coverage Requirements\n\n- board surfaceлҠ” add/delete/search/helper/status/metadata кҙҖл Ё copyлҘј лӘЁл‘җ dictionaryлЎң м ңкіөн•ҙм•ј н•ңлӢӨ.\n- category surfaceлҠ” icon action tooltip/aria label, ordering helper, disabled explanationмқ„ localeлЎң м ңкіөн•ҙм•ј н•ңлӢӨ.\n- shell surfaceлҠ” latest chip fallback, menu helper, feedback copyлҘј localeлЎң м ңкіөн•ҙм•ј н•ңлӢӨ.\n- detail/history/report/workflow surfaceлҠ” stage/status/metric labelкіј helper/empty copyк°Җ locale bypass мғҒнғңлЎң лӮЁм§Җ м•Ҡм•„м•ј н•ңлӢӨ.\n- settings surfaceлҠ” language/theme/helper/field action copyк°Җ ko/enм—җм„ң к°ҷмқҖ мқҳлҜёлҘј мң м§Җн•ҙм•ј н•ңлӢӨ.\n\n## Derived Label Rules\n\n- `dashboardShell.ts` к°ҷмқҖ helperм—җм„ң мЎ°н•©лҗҳлҠ” stage/status/metric labelмқҖ locale consumerлҘј нҶөн•ҙ мғқм„ұн•ҙм•ј н•ңлӢӨ.\n- `done`, `current`, `upcoming`, `blocked`, `in progress` к°ҷмқҖ нҢҢмғқ лқјлІЁмқҖ inline English кі м •к°’мңјлЎң лӮЁм§Җ м•Ҡм•„м•ј н•ңлӢӨ.\n- version fallback, missing/unknown fallback, latest chip fallbackлҸ„ locale-awareм—¬м•ј н•ңлӢӨ.\n\n## Non-Requirements\n\n- dashboard мҷёл¶Җ app/package м „мІҙмқҳ locale мІҙкі„ к°ңнҺё\n- мқҙлІҲ topicм—җм„ң мғҲ м–ём–ҙ м¶”к°Җ\n- copywriting л°©н–Ҙмқ„ м „л©ҙ мһ¬лёҢлһңл”©н•ҳлҠ” кІғ\n",
