ures/backlog/BacklogWorkspace.tsx` | `implementation/diffs/006_CREATE_apps_dashboard_src_features_backlog_BacklogWorkspace_tsx.diff` | `T3,T6` | dense row backlog workspace, toolbar filters, section collapse, row metadata surfaceлҘј м¶”к°Җ |\n| 007 | CREATE | `apps/dashboard/src/features/backlog/InsightsRail.tsx` | `implementation/diffs/007_CREATE_apps_dashboard_src_features_backlog_InsightsRail_tsx.diff` | `T4,T5,T6` | docked `Backlog Insights` railкіј workload/trend/progress widget stackмқ„ м¶”к°Җ |\n| 008 | UPDATE | `apps/dashboard/src/app/DashboardApp.tsx` | `implementation/diffs/008_UPDATE_apps_dashboard_src_app_DashboardApp_tsx.diff` | `T1,T2,T3,T4,T5,T6` | м „мІҙ dashboard shellмқ„ Jira insightsнҳ• layoutмңјлЎң мһ¬кө¬м„ұн•ҳкі  board/reports/settingsлҘј мғҲ shell м•Ҳм—җ мһ¬л°°м№ҳ |\n| 009 | UPDATE | `apps/dashboard/src/shared/model/dashboard.ts` | `implementation/diffs/009_UPDATE_apps_dashboard_src_shared_model_dashboard_ts.refactor.diff` | `T6` | backlog rowмҷҖ insights widgetмқҙ кіөмҡ©мңјлЎң м“°лҠ” tone contractлҘј shared modelлЎң мҠ№кІ©н–ҲлӢӨ |\n| 010 | UPDATE | `apps/dashboard/src/app/dashboardShell.ts` | `implementation/diffs/010_UPDATE_apps_dashboard_src_app_dashboardShell_ts.refactor.diff` | `T1,T4,T6` | app helperк°Җ app-local tone alias лҢҖмӢ  shared dashboard toneмқ„ м“°лҸ„лЎқ мқҳмЎҙм„ұмқ„ м •лҰ¬н–ҲлӢӨ |\n| 011 | UPDATE | `apps/dashboard/src/features/backlog/BacklogWorkspace.tsx` | `implementation/diffs/011_UPDATE_apps_dashboard_src_features_backlog_BacklogWorkspace_tsx.refactor.diff` | `T3,T6` | backlog row chip/dot tone кі„мӮ°мқ„ shared helperлЎң мң„мһ„н•ҙ component лӮҙл¶Җ нҶ нҒ° мӨ‘ліөмқ„ м ңкұ°н–ҲлӢӨ |\n| 012 | UPDATE | `apps/dashboard/src/features/backlog/InsightsRail.tsx` | `implementation/diffs/012_UPDATE_apps_dashboard_src_features_backlog_InsightsRail_tsx.refactor.diff` | `T4,T6` | rail widget accent color кі„мӮ°мқ„ shared tone helperлЎң нҶөн•©н•ҙ widget mapping мқјкҙҖм„ұмқ„ лҶ’мҳҖлӢӨ |\n| 013 | CREATE | `apps/dashboard/src/shared/theme/dash