+                    "title": "spec/ui/artifact-inspector.md",
+                    "sourcePath": "poggn/archive/dashboard-renewal/spec/ui/artifact-inspector.md",
+                    "content": "---\npgg:\n  topic: \"dashboard-renewal\"\n  stage: \"plan\"\n  status: \"reviewed\"\n  skill: \"pgg-plan\"\n  score: 95\n  updated_at: \"2026-04-21T15:55:16Z\"\nreactflow:\n  node_id: \"spec-artifact-inspector\"\n  node_type: \"doc\"\n  label: \"spec/ui/artifact-inspector.md\"\nstate:\n  summary: \"topic artifact inspector panelкіј detail modal лҸҷмһ‘мқ„ м •мқҳн•ңлӢӨ.\"\n  next: \"task.md мҠ№мқё\"\n---\n\n# Artifact Inspector Spec\n\n## Goal\n\n- topic card лҳҗлҠ” workflow nodeм—җм„ң drill-downн•ң artifactлҘј мқҪкё° м „мҡ© inspector panelкіј modalм—җм„ң мқјкҙҖлҗҳкІҢ ліҙм—¬мЈјлҠ” кі„м•Ҫмқ„ м •мқҳн•ңлӢӨ.\n\n## Artifact Groups\n\n- lifecycle docs: `proposal.md`, `plan.md`, `task.md`, `state/current.md`\n- review docs: `reviews/proposal.review.md`, `reviews/plan.review.md`, `reviews/task.review.md`, `reviews/code.review.md`, `reviews/refactor.review.md`, `reviews/qa.review.md`\n- implementation docs: `implementation/index.md`, `implementation/diffs/*.diff`\n- qa docs: `qa/report.md`, `qa/test-plan.md`, `qa/test-result.md`, `qa/review.md`\n- release docs: `version.json`, `workflow.reactflow.json`, `state/history.ndjson`\n\n## Inspector Rules\n\n- inspectorлҠ” м„ нғқлҗң topicмқҳ artifact group summaryмҷҖ нҳ„мһ¬ м„ нғқ artifact detailмқ„ н•Ёк»ҳ ліҙм—¬мӨҖлӢӨ.\n- group summaryлҠ” мЎҙмһ¬ м—¬л¶Җ, мөңмӢ  updatedAt, к°ңмҲҳ, лҢҖн‘ң мғҒнғңлҘј ліҙм—¬мӨҖлӢӨ.\n- detail contentлҠ” markdown, diff, plain textлҘј кө¬л¶„н•ҙ н‘ңмӢңн•ҙм•ј н•ңлӢӨ.\n- `version.json` лҳҗлҠ” publish metadataк°Җ м—ҶлҠ” archive topicлҸ„ partial мғҒнғңлЎң мІҳлҰ¬н•ҙм•ј н•ңлӢӨ.\n\n## Detail Interaction\n\n- topic cardм—җм„ң л°”лЎң лҢҖн‘ң artifactлҘј м—ҙ мҲҳ мһҲм–ҙм•ј н•ңлӢӨ.\n- workflow node м„ нғқкіј inspector selectionмқҖ к°ҷмқҖ detail payloadлҘј кіөмң н•  мҲҳ мһҲм–ҙм•ј н•ңлӢӨ.\n- кёҙ л¬ём„ңлҠ” scrollable panel лҳҗлҠ” modalлЎң ліҙм—¬мЈјкі  raw pathлҘј н•Ёк»ҳ н‘ңмӢңн•ңлӢӨ.\n- detailмқҙ м—ҶлҠ” кІҪмҡ° unavailable л©”мӢңм§ҖмҷҖ source pathл§Ң ліҙм—¬мӨҖлӢӨ.\n\n## UI Boundaries\n\n- inspectorлҠ” нҢҢмқј нҺём§‘кё°лҘј лҢҖмІҙн•ҳм§Җ м•ҠлҠ”лӢӨ.\n- markdown л ҢлҚ”л§ҒмқҖ мӣҗл¬ё ліҙмЎҙкіј к°ҖлҸ…м„ұмқҳ к· нҳ•мқ„ мҡ°м„ н•ңлӢӨ.\n- diff viewerлҠ” м¶”к°Җ/мӮӯм ң кө¬л¶„мқҙ к°ҖлҠҘн•ҙм•ј н•ҳм§Җл§Ң git blameлӮҳ inline editлҠ” лІ”мң„м—җм„ң м ңмҷён•ңлӢӨ.\n\n## Non-Requirements\n\n- WYSIWYG л¬ём„ң нҺём§‘\n- arbitrary local file browse\n- full git history viewer\n",
