ry, document list, inspector preview, full dialog viewerлҘј workflow node clickкіј м—°кІ° |\n| T-006 | snapshot/data adapter, locale, empty/error state, responsive behaviorлҘј нҶөн•©н•ҳкі  verification кІ°кіјлҘј кё°лЎқн•ңлӢӨ | `spec/ui/project-list-board.md`, `spec/ui/project-detail-workspace.md`, `spec/ui/topic-lifecycle-board.md`, `spec/ui/artifact-inspector.md`, `spec/infra/dashboard-topic-artifact-snapshot.md`, `spec/infra/dashboard-feature-architecture.md` | done | `packages/core` snapshotм—җ archive/artifact л©”нғҖлҘј м¶”к°Җн•ҳкі  workspace build + snapshot мһ¬мғқм„ұмңјлЎң нҶөн•© кІҖмҰқ |\n\n## Audit Applicability\n\n- `pgg-token`: `not_required` | task л¶„н•ҙ лӢЁкі„мқҙл©° token auditмқ„ м—ҙ к·јкұ°к°Җ м—ҶлӢӨ\n- `pgg-performance`: `not_required` | м„ұлҠҘ мёЎм • лҢҖмғҒ кө¬нҳ„мқҙлӮҳ verification contract ліҖкІҪмқҙ м•„м§Ғ м—ҶлӢӨ\n",
