                     "content": "---\npgg:\n  topic: \"pgg-dirty-worktree-baseline\"\n  stage: \"qa\"\n  status: \"done\"\n  skill: \"pgg-qa\"\n  score: 97\n  updated_at: \"2026-04-23T01:57:33Z\"\nreactflow:\n  node_id: \"qa-report\"\n  node_type: \"review\"\n  label: \"qa/report.md\"\nstate:\n  summary: \"dirty worktree baseline fixм—җ лҢҖн•ң QAмҷҖ нҡҢк·Җ кІҖмҰқмқ„ кё°лЎқн•ңлӢӨ.\"\n  next: \"archive ready\"\n---\n\n# QA Report\n\n## Scope\n\n- topic мғқм„ұ мӢң dirty worktree baseline нҢҢмқјмқҙ кё°лЎқлҗҳлҠ”м§Җ нҷ•мқё\n- stage commit helperк°Җ baseline unrelated dirtyлҠ” л¬ҙмӢңн•ҳкі  мғҲ unrelated dirtyлҠ” кі„мҶҚ м°ЁлӢЁн•ҳлҠ”м§Җ нҷ•мқё\n- archive publish helperк°Җ к°ҷмқҖ baseline к·ңм№ҷмқ„ кіөмң н•ҳлҠ”м§Җ нҷ•мқё\n- helper/template/doc/test ліҖкІҪмқҙ buildмҷҖ core testм—җм„ң н•Ёк»ҳ нҶөкіјн•ҳлҠ”м§Җ нҷ•мқё\n\n## Results\n\n| ID | Case | Result | Evidence |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| QA-001 | baseline нҢҢмқј кі„м•Ҫ л°ҳмҳҒ | pass | `.codex/sh/pgg-new-topic.sh`, `.codex/add/WOKR-FLOW.md`, `.codex/add/STATE-CONTRACT.md`, `state/dirty-worktree-baseline.txt` |\n| QA-002 | stage helper baseline н—Ҳмҡ© | pass | `packages/core/test/git-publish.test.mjs`мқҳ `stage commit helper ignores pre-existing unrelated dirty files recorded in the baseline` |\n| QA-003 | archive helper baseline н—Ҳмҡ© | pass | `packages/core/test/git-publish.test.mjs`мқҳ `archive helper ignores pre-existing unrelated dirty files recorded in the baseline` |\n| QA-004 | source/dist/template лҸҷкё°нҷ” | pass | `pnpm build` |\n| QA-005 | м „мІҙ core нҡҢк·Җ | pass | `pnpm test` |\n\n## Expert Notes\n\n| Expert | Score | Summary | Blocking |\n|---|---:|---|---|\n| QA/н…ҢмҠӨнҠё м—”м§ҖлӢҲм–ҙ | 97 | baseline capture, stage guard, archive guardлҘј к°Ғк°Ғ fixtureлЎң кІҖмҰқн–Ҳкі  м „мІҙ core testлҸ„ нҶөкіјн–ҲлӢӨ. | м—ҶмқҢ |\n| мҪ”л“ң лҰ¬л·°м–ҙ | 96 | helperмҷҖ template, docs, testsк°Җ к°ҷмқҖ кі„м•ҪмңјлЎң м •л ¬лҗҳм–ҙ нҳ„мһ¬ repoмҷҖ мғқм„ұ repoмқҳ лҸҷмһ‘ м°Ёмқҙк°Җ мӨ„м—ҲлӢӨ. | м—ҶмқҢ |\n| SRE / мҡҙмҳҒ м—”м§ҖлӢҲм–ҙ | 97 | кё°м