                     "content": "---\npgg:\n  topic: \"pgg-reframe-token-and-performance-as-conditional-audits\"\n  stage: \"qa\"\n  status: \"done\"\n  skill: \"pgg-qa\"\n  score: 96\n  updated_at: \"2026-04-21T14:05:39Z\"\n---\n\n# QA Report\n\n## Test Plan\n\n- core workflowк°Җ `pgg-add -> pgg-plan -> pgg-code -> pgg-refactor -> pgg-qa`лЎң кі м •лҗҳкі , `pgg-token`/`pgg-performance`к°Җ optional audit branchлЎңл§Ң лӢӨлӨ„м§ҖлҠ”м§Җ л¬ём„ң/мғҒнғң/outputм—җм„ң нҷ•мқён•ңлӢӨ.\n- required auditмқё `token/report.md`к°Җ мЎҙмһ¬н•ҳкі , `not_required` auditмқё `pgg-performance`к°Җ blockingм—җм„ң м ңмҷёлҗҳлҠ”м§Җ нҷ•мқён•ңлӢӨ.\n- trusted helper кё°мӨҖмңјлЎң `pgg-qa` gateк°Җ нҶөкіјн•ҳкі  archive preconditionмқё `qa/report.md` мғҒнғңмҷҖ `state/current.md` stageк°Җ мқјм№ҳн•ҳлҸ„лЎқ м •лҰ¬н•ңлӢӨ.\n- current-project verification contractк°Җ `manual`мқҙл©ҙ мһҗлҸҷ м ңн’Ҳ кІҖмҰқ лҢҖмӢ  `manual verification required`лҘј лӘ…мӢңн•ңлӢӨ.\n\n## Execution Results\n\n- `reviews/code.review.md`\n  - нҶөкіј. `pnpm build`, `pnpm build:readme`, `node packages/cli/dist/index.js update --cwd /config/workspace/poggn-ai`, `pnpm test`, helper fixture кІҖмҰқмқҙ мқҙлҜё кё°лЎқлҸј мһҲлӢӨ.\n- `reviews/refactor.review.md`\n  - нҶөкіј. `packages/core/src/templates.ts` лӮҙл¶Җ helper м¶”м¶ңлЎң audit applicability/verification contract мӨ‘ліөмқҙ мӨ„м—Ҳкі  blocking issueк°Җ м—ҶлӢӨ.\n- `token/report.md`\n  - нҶөкіј. naive full-doc handoff `5617` estimated tokens лҢҖл№„ `state/current.md` `778`, `pgg-state-pack.sh` `569`лЎң token м Ҳк°җ к·јкұ°к°Җ кё°лЎқлҸј мһҲлӢӨ.\n- `pgg-performance`\n  - л№„м°ЁлӢЁ. `state/current.md`мқҳ `Audit Applicability`м—җм„ң `not_required`мқҙкі  `.pgg/project.json`мқҳ verification contractлҸ„ `manual`мқҙлқј мқҙлІҲ topicмқҳ blocking QA лҢҖмғҒмқҙ м•„лӢҲлӢӨ.\n- `./.codex/sh/pgg-gate.sh pgg-qa pgg-reframe-token-and-performance-as-conditional-audits`\n  - нҶөкіј. нҳ„мһ¬ topicмқҙ QA м§„мһ… мЎ°кұҙмқ„ л§ҢмЎұн•ңлӢӨ.\n- current-project verification contract\n  - `manual verification required`. `.pgg/project.json`мқҳ `verification.mode`к°Җ `manual`, `commands`к°Җ л№Ҳ л°°м—ҙмқҙл©° `manualReason`мқҖ `verification contract not declared`лӢӨ.\n\n## Test Evidence\n\n- QA gate: `{\"gate\":\"pass\",\"stage\":\"pgg-qa\"}`\n- token кё°мӨҖм„ : full-doc handoff `5617` estimated tokens, `state/current.md` `778`, `pgg-state-pack.sh` `569`\n- optional audit applicability:\n  - `pgg-token`: `required`\n  - `pgg-performance`: `not_required`\n- manual verification status: `.pgg/project.json`м—җм„ң `verification contract not declared`\n\n## Expert Notes\n\n| Expert | Score | Core Judgment | Evidence Checked | Blocking Issue |\n|---|---:|---|---|---|\n| QA/н…ҢмҠӨнҠё м—”м§ҖлӢҲм–ҙ | 96 | required token auditмҷҖ QA gate, prior implementation verification evidenceк°Җ лӘЁл‘җ м—°кІ°лҸј мһҲм–ҙ workflow contract ліҖкІҪ topicмңјлЎңм„ңлҠ” pass нҢҗм •мқҙ к°ҖлҠҘн•ҳлӢӨ. | `reviews/code.review.md`, `token/report.md`, `pgg-qa` gate кІ°кіј, `.pgg/project.json`мқ„ нҷ•мқён–ҲлӢӨ. | м—ҶмқҢ |\n| мҪ”л“ң лҰ¬л·°м–ҙ | 96 | core workflowмҷҖ optional audit contractк°Җ source-of-truth, helper, generated docs, topic stateм—җ мқјкҙҖлҗҳкІҢ л°ҳмҳҒлҗҗлӢӨ. | `reviews/refactor.review.md`, `implementation/index.md`, `state/current.md`, `workflow.reactflow.json`мқ„ нҷ•мқён–ҲлӢӨ. | м—ҶмқҢ |\n| SRE / мҡҙмҳҒ м—”м§ҖлӢҲм–ҙ | 95 | verification contractлҠ” м—¬м „нһҲ мҲҳлҸҷмқҙм§Җл§Ң к·ё м ңм•Ҫмқҙ stateмҷҖ QA кё°лЎқм—җ лӘ…мӢңлҸј мһҲм–ҙ мҡҙмҳҒмғҒ мҳӨнҢҗ к°ҖлҠҘм„ұмқҖ лӮ®лӢӨ. | `.pgg/project.json`, `state/current.md`, `token/report.md`лҘј нҷ•мқён–ҲлӢӨ. | м—ҶмқҢ |\n\n## Decision\n\n- pass\n\n## Notes\n\n- current-project verification contractк°Җ м„ м–ёлҗҳм§Җ м•Ҡм•„ м¶”к°Җ м ңн’Ҳ/м•ұ мҲҳмӨҖ мһҗлҸҷ кІҖмҰқмқҖ мҲҳн–үн•ҳм§Җ м•Ҡм•ҳкі  `manual verification required`лЎң лӮЁкёҙлӢӨ.\n- `pgg-performance`лҠ” `not_required`мқҙлҜҖлЎң мқҙлІҲ topicмқҳ archive blocking мЎ°кұҙмқҙ м•„лӢҲлӢӨ.\n",
