                     "content": "---\npgg:\n  topic: \"pgg-release-branch-publish-and-semver-strategy\"\n  stage: \"qa\"\n  status: \"done\"\n  skill: \"pgg-qa\"\n  score: 96\n  updated_at: \"2026-04-22T03:06:06Z\"\n---\n\n# QA Report\n\n## Test Plan\n\n- `ai/<archive_type>/<target-version>-<short-name>`мҷҖ `release/<target-version>-<short-name>` contractк°Җ helper, ledger, publish metadataм—җ к°ҷмқҖ мқҳлҜёлЎң м—°кІ°лҗҳлҠ”м§Җ нҷ•мқён•ңлӢӨ.\n- `version_bump`к°Җ `archive_type`мҷҖ л¶„лҰ¬лҗҳм–ҙ semverмҷҖ branch naming source-of-truthлЎң мһ‘лҸҷн•ҳлҠ”м§Җ нҷ•мқён•ңлӢӨ.\n- `main` direct push кёҲм§Җ, dirty worktree/remote лҜём„Өм • guardrail, release branch review metadataк°Җ нҡҢк·Җ н…ҢмҠӨнҠёмҷҖ dashboard surfaceм—җ лӮЁлҠ”м§Җ нҷ•мқён•ңлӢӨ.\n- current-project verification contractк°Җ м„ м–ёлҗҳм§Җ м•ҠмқҖ мғҒнғңлҘј QA к·јкұ°м—җ лӘ…мӢңн•ҳкі  optional audit blocking м—¬л¶ҖлҘј м җкІҖн•ңлӢӨ.\n\n## Audit Applicability\n\n- [pgg-token]: [not_required] | token л№„мҡ© мёЎм • topicмқҙ м•„лӢҲлқј branch lifecycleкіј semver contract кІҖмҰқмқҙ мӨ‘мӢ¬мқҙлӢӨ.\n- [pgg-performance]: [not_required] | м„ұлҠҘ мёЎм •мқҙ м•„лӢҲлқј helper semantics, ledger, dashboard release metadata нҡҢк·Җ кІҖмҰқмқҙлӢӨ.\n\n## Execution Results\n\n- `reviews/code.review.md`\n  - нҶөкіј. кө¬нҳ„ лІ”мң„ м „мІҙм—җм„ң blocking issueк°Җ м—Ҷкі  helper/analyzer/dashboard/testк°Җ к°ҷмқҖ кі„м•Ҫмқ„ л”°лҘёлӢӨ.\n- `pnpm build`\n  - нҶөкіј. workspace buildмҷҖ dashboard production buildк°Җ м„ұкіөн–ҲлӢӨ.\n- `pnpm test`\n  - нҶөкіј. `packages/core` 16к°ң н…ҢмҠӨнҠёк°Җ лӘЁл‘җ нҶөкіјн–Ҳкі  `git-publish.test.mjs`м—җм„ң release branch push, main guardrail, invalid message, fallback precedenceлҘј мһ¬нҳ„н–ҲлӢӨ.\n- `pnpm build:readme`\n  - нҶөкіј. root README мғқм„ұмқҙ мғҲ release branchмҷҖ `version_bump` л¬ёкө¬ кё°мӨҖмңјлЎң мң м§ҖлҗңлӢӨ.\n- `node packages/cli/dist/index.js update --cwd /config/workspace/poggn-ai`\n  - нҶөкіј. managed helper/skill/doc sync кІ°кіјк°Җ `unchanged`лЎң мң м§ҖлҸј generator driftк°Җ м—ҶлӢӨ.\n- current-project verification contract\n  - `manual verification required`. `.pgg/project.json`мқҳ `verification.mode`к°Җ `manual`, `commands`к°Җ л№Ҳ л°°м—ҙмқҙкі  `manualReason`мқҖ `verification contract not declared`лӢӨ.\n- git publish preflight\n  - expected ai branchлЎң мқҙлҸҷн–ҲлӢӨ: `ai/feat/0.6.0-pgg-release-branch-publish-and-semver-strategy`.\n  - нҳ„мһ¬ worktreeм—җлҠ” topic лІ”мң„ л°–мқҳ `apps/dashboard/vite.config.ts`, `poggn/version-history.ndjson` dirty changeк°Җ лӮЁм•„ мһҲм–ҙ archive л’Ө automatic release publishлҠ” `publish_blocked`лЎң кё°лЎқлҗ  к°ҖлҠҘм„ұмқҙ лҶ’лӢӨ.\n\n## Test Evidence\n\n- build: `pnpm build`\n- regression: `pnpm test` кё°мӨҖ 16 tests passed, 0 failed\n- readme sync: `pnpm build:readme`\n- managed sync: `node packages/cli/dist/index.js update --cwd /config/workspace/poggn-ai` returned `status=unchanged`\n- manual verification status: `.pgg/project.json`мқҳ `verification.mode=manual`, `manualReason=verification contract not declared`\n- git preflight branch: `git branch --show-current` => `ai/feat/0.6.0-pgg-release-branch-publish-and-semver-strategy`\n\n## Expert Notes\n\n| Expert | Score | Core Judgment | Evidence Checked | Blocking Issue |\n|---|---:|---|---|---|\n| QA/н…ҢмҠӨнҠё м—”м§ҖлӢҲм–ҙ | 96 | release branch publishмҷҖ `version_bump` semver regression proofк°Җ л№Ңл“ңмҷҖ core н…ҢмҠӨнҠёлЎң м¶©л¶„нһҲ мһ¬нҳ„лҗҳм–ҙ QA pass к°ҖлҠҘн•ҳлӢӨ. | `pnpm build`, `pnpm test`, `packages/core/test/git-publish.test.mjs`, `packages/core/test/version-history.test.mjs`лҘј нҷ•мқён–ҲлӢӨ. | м—ҶмқҢ |\n| мҪ”л“ң лҰ¬л·°м–ҙ | 96 | source-of-truthк°Җ `packages/core/src/templates.ts`м—җ мң м§Җлҗҳкі  analyzer/dashboard surfaceк°Җ publish metadataлҘј мқҪлҸ„лЎқ м •л ¬лҸј мһҲлӢӨ. | `packages/core/src/templates.ts`, `packages/core/src/index.ts`, `apps/dashboard/src/**`, `reviews/code.review.md`лҘј нҷ•мқён–ҲлӢӨ. | м—ҶмқҢ |\n| SRE / мҡҙмҳҒ м—”м§ҖлӢҲм–ҙ | 95 | verification contractлҠ” мҲҳлҸҷ мғҒнғңлЎң лӘ…нҷ•н•ҳкі , dirty worktree guardrailмқҙ archive нӣ„ release publishлҘј м°ЁлӢЁн•ҳлҠ”м§Җ metadataлЎң нҷ•мқён•  мҲҳ мһҲлӢӨ. | `.pgg/project.json`, `git status --short`, `state/current.md`лҘј нҷ•мқён–ҲлӢӨ. | м—ҶмқҢ |\n\n## Decision\n\n- pass\n\n## Git Publish Message\n\n- title: Release branch publish strategy\n- why: main м§Ғм ‘ pushлҘј л§үкі  ai/release branch lifecycleкіј semver кё°мӨҖмқ„ л¶„лҰ¬н•ҙм•ј workflowк°Җ м•Ҳм „н•ҙм§„лӢӨ.\n- footer: Refs: pgg-release-branch-publish-and-semver-strategy\n\n## Notes\n\n- current-project verification contractк°Җ м„ м–ёлҗҳм§Җ м•Ҡм•„ м ңн’Ҳ мҲҳмӨҖ мһҗлҸҷ кІҖмҰқмқҖ м¶”к°Җ мӢӨн–үн•ҳм§Җ м•Ҡм•ҳкі  `manual verification required`лЎң лӮЁкёҙлӢӨ.\n- `pgg-token`, `pgg-performance`лҠ” л‘ҳ лӢӨ `not_required`мқҙлҜҖлЎң archive blocking лҢҖмғҒмқҙ м•„лӢҲлӢӨ.\n- archive helperлҠ” topic кІҖмҰқмқҙ passм—¬лҸ„ topic лІ”мң„ л°– dirty changeк°Җ лӮЁм•„ мһҲмңјл©ҙ release publishлҘј л§үмқ„ мҲҳ мһҲмңјл©°, мқҙлІҲ runм—җм„ңлҸ„ к·ё кІ°кіјлҘј metadataлЎң лӮЁкё°лҠ”м§Җ нҷ•мқёмқҙ н•„мҡ”н•ҳлӢӨ.\n",
