°ұм—…н–ҲлӢӨ. helper/skill нҢҢмқј мһҗмІҙлҠ” `unchanged`мҳҖкі  мқҙлІҲ topic кө¬нҳ„ кі„м•Ҫмқ„ к№ЁлҠ” failureлҠ” м•„лӢҲлҜҖлЎң QA blockerлЎң ліҙм§Җ м•ҠлҠ”лӢӨ.\n- current-project verification contract\n  - `manual verification required`. `.pgg/project.json`мқҳ `verification.mode`к°Җ `manual`, `commands`к°Җ л№Ҳ л°°м—ҙмқҙкі  `manualReason`мқҖ `verification contract not declared`лӢӨ.\n- git publish preflight\n  - expected ai branchлЎң мң м§Җ мӨ‘мқҙлӢӨ: `ai/fix/0.6.1-release-alias`.\n  - нҳ„мһ¬ worktreeм—җлҠ” topic лІ”мң„ л°– `apps/dashboard/vite.config.ts`, `poggn/version-history.ndjson` dirty changeк°Җ лӮЁм•„ мһҲм–ҙ archive л’Ө automatic release publishлҠ” `publish_blocked`лЎң кё°лЎқлҗ  к°ҖлҠҘм„ұмқҙ лҶ’лӢӨ.\n\n## Test Evidence\n\n- build: `pnpm build`\n- regression: `pnpm test` кё°мӨҖ 19 tests passed, 0 failed\n- readme sync: `pnpm build:readme`\n- managed sync: `node packages/cli/dist/index.js update --cwd /config/workspace/poggn-ai` returned `status=conflicted`, conflict backup created for `.codex/add/WOKR-FLOW.md`\n- manual verification status: `.pgg/project.json`мқҳ `verification.mode=manual`, `manualReason=verification contract not declared`\n- git preflight branch: `git branch --show-current` => `ai/fix/0.6.1-release-alias`\n\n## Expert Notes\n\n| Expert | Score | Core Judgment | Evidence Checked | Blocking Issue |\n|---|---:|---|---|---|\n| QA/н…ҢмҠӨнҠё м—”м§ҖлӢҲм–ҙ | 96 | first publish/update publish, concise alias, cleanup timing regression proofк°Җ core н…ҢмҠӨнҠёмҷҖ build evidenceлЎң м¶©л¶„нһҲ мһ¬нҳ„лҗҳм–ҙ QA pass к°ҖлҠҘн•ҳлӢӨ. | `pnpm build`, `pnpm test`, `packages/core/test/git-publish.test.mjs`, `packages/core/test/version-history.test.mjs`лҘј нҷ•мқён–ҲлӢӨ. | м—ҶмқҢ |\n| мҪ”л“ң лҰ¬л·°м–ҙ | 96 | source-of-truthк°Җ `packages/core/src/templates.ts`м—җ мң м§Җлҗҳкі  runtime, dashboard, README surfaceк°Җ к°ҷмқҖ lifecycle metadataлҘј мқҪлҸ„лЎқ м •л ¬лҸј мһҲлӢӨ. | `packages/core/src/templates.ts`, `packages/core/src/index.ts`, `apps/dashboard/src/**`, `reviews/code.review.md`лҘј нҷ•мқён–ҲлӢӨ. | м—ҶмқҢ |\n| SRE / мҡҙмҳҒ м—”м§ҖлӢҲм–ҙ | 95 | verification contractлҠ” manual мғҒнғңлЎң лӘ…нҷ•н•ҳкі , unrelated dirty worktreeк°Җ archive нӣ„ release publishлҘј м°ЁлӢЁн•  мҲҳ мһҲлӢӨлҠ” мҡҙмҳҒ лҰ¬мҠӨнҒ¬к°Җ metadataлЎң м¶”м Ғ к°ҖлҠҘн•ҳлӢӨ. | `.pgg/project.json`, `git status --short`, `state/current.md`, update conflict outputмқ„ нҷ•мқён–ҲлӢӨ. | м—ҶмқҢ |\n\n## Decision\n\n- pass\n\n## Git Publish Message\n\n- title: Release upstream alias fix\n- why: QA pass л’Ө release branch first push, working branch removal timing, concise alias к·ңм№ҷмқ„ к°ҷмқҙ ліҙмҷ„н•ҙм•ј branch lifecycleмқҙ мӢӨмӮ¬мҡ© нқҗлҰ„кіј л§һлҠ”лӢӨ.\n- footer: Refs: pgg-release-upstream-and-compact-branch-alias\n\n## Notes\n\n- current-project verification contractк°Җ м„ м–ёлҗҳм§Җ м•Ҡм•„ м ңн’Ҳ мҲҳмӨҖ мһҗлҸҷ кІҖмҰқмқҖ м¶”к°Җ мӢӨн–үн•ҳм§Җ м•Ҡм•ҳкі  `manual verification required`лЎң лӮЁкёҙлӢӨ.\n- `pgg-token`, `pgg-performance`лҠ” л‘ҳ лӢӨ `not_required`мқҙлҜҖлЎң archive blocking лҢҖмғҒмқҙ м•„лӢҲлӢӨ.\n- `update` conflictлҠ” generator-managed л¬ём„ң мӮ¬мҡ©мһҗ мҲҳм • л°ұм—… мқҙмҠҲмқҙл©° helper/runtime/source-of-truth drift failureмҷҖлҠ” кө¬л¶„н•ҙм„ң м¶”м Ғн•ңлӢӨ.\n- archive helperлҠ” topic кІҖмҰқмқҙ passм—¬лҸ„ topic лІ”мң„ л°– dirty changeк°Җ лӮЁм•„ мһҲмңјл©ҙ release publishлҘј л§үмқ„ мҲҳ мһҲмңјл©°, мқҙлІҲ runм—җм„ңлҸ„ к·ё кІ°кіјлҘј metadataлЎң лӮЁкё°лҠ”м§Җ нҷ•мқёмқҙ н•„мҡ”н•ҳлӢӨ.\n",
