implementation diffлҠ” reconstructed original кё°л°ҳ unified diffлЎң кё°лЎқн–ҲлӢӨ.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `rg -n \"task\\\\.review\\\\.md|Absolute Gate|нҷ•мқё к·јкұ°|мҰқкұ°|м •л§җлЎң мқҙ кө¬нҳ„мқҙ мҳ¬л°”лҘёк°Җмҡ”|м •л§җ мқҙкІғмқҙ мһ‘лҸҷлҗҳлҠ” кІғмқҙ л§һлӮҳмҡ”\" .codex/add .codex/skills .codex/sh/pgg-gate.sh`\n- `./.codex/sh/pgg-gate.sh pgg-code pgg-review-attribution-and-proof-first-qa-guardrails`\n- `cp -R poggn/active/pgg-review-attribution-and-proof-first-qa-guardrails /tmp/pgg-review-attribution-gate-check`\n- `mv /tmp/pgg-review-attribution-gate-check/reviews/task.review.md /tmp/pgg-review-attribution-gate-check/reviews/task.review.md.bak`\n- `./.codex/sh/pgg-gate.sh pgg-code /tmp/pgg-review-attribution-gate-check`\n\n## Summary\n\n- future default contractм—җм„ң `task.review.md` н•„мҲҳ мҡ”кө¬к°Җ м ңкұ°лҗҳм—ҲлӢӨ.\n- reviewмҷҖ QAлҠ” proof-first м ҲлҢҖ мЎ°кұҙ, м „л¬ёк°Җ attribution, нҷ•мқё к·јкұ°лҘј кё°ліё нҳ•мӢқмңјлЎң к°–кІҢ лҗҳм—ҲлӢӨ.\n- `state/current.md` мөңмҶҢ handoff мӣҗм№ҷмқҖ мң м§Җлҗҳм—ҲлӢӨ.\n",
