                     "content": "---\npgg:\n  topic: \"pgg-shell-auto-run-and-interactive-change-exit\"\n  stage: \"qa\"\n  status: \"done\"\n  skill: \"pgg-qa\"\n  score: 98\n  updated_at: \"2026-04-21T04:38:21Z\"\nreactflow:\n  node_id: \"qa-report\"\n  node_type: \"review\"\n  label: \"qa/report.md\"\nstate:\n  summary: \"trusted `.codex/sh` helper кі„м•Ҫкіј interactive мў…лЈҢ/н‘ңкё° ліҖкІҪм—җ лҢҖн•ң QAлҘј нҶөн•© ліҙкі м„ңлЎң кё°лЎқн•ңлӢӨ.\"\n  next: \"archive complete\"\n---\n\n# QA Report\n\n## Scope\n\n- trusted `.codex/sh/*.sh` helper лІ”мң„к°Җ л¬ём„ң, generated source, current workspace л¬ём„ңм—җ мқјкҙҖлҗҳкІҢ л°ҳмҳҒлҗҳм—ҲлҠ”м§Җ нҷ•мқё\n- `init`, `teams`, `lang`, `auto` кІ°кіјк°Җ changed/unchanged мғҒнғңмҷҖ path-level summaryлҘј м¶ңл Ҙн•ҳлҠ”м§Җ нҷ•мқё\n- interactive `teams` м„ нғқмқҙ PTYм—җм„ң `changed`мҷҖ `cancelled` мғҒнғңлҘј м¶ңл Ҙн•ҳкі  мў…лЈҢн•ҳлҠ”м§Җ нҷ•мқё\n- `pgg-code`мҷҖ `pgg-qa` gate, build, archive helper мӢӨн–ү мЎ°кұҙмқҙ м¶©мЎұлҗҳлҠ”м§Җ нҷ•мқё\n\n## Results\n\n| ID | Case | Result | Evidence |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| QA-001 | code/qa gate нҶөкіј | pass | `./.codex/sh/pgg-gate.sh pgg-code pgg-shell-auto-run-and-interactive-change-exit`, `./.codex/sh/pgg-gate.sh pgg-qa pgg-shell-auto-run-and-interactive-change-exit` |\n| QA-002 | source build лҸҷкё°нҷ” | pass | `pnpm build` |\n| QA-003 | sample init summary | pass | `node packages/cli/dist/index.js init --cwd /tmp/pgg-shell-auto-run-and-interactive-change-exit-qa --provider codex --lang ko --auto on --teams off` -> `status=changed`, created includes `.pgg/project.json` |\n| QA-004 | teams changed/unchanged summary | pass | `node packages/cli/dist/index.js teams --cwd /tmp/pgg-shell-auto-run-and-interactive-change-exit-qa --value on` -> `status=changed`, second run -> `status=unchanged` |\n| QA-005 | lang summary with generated doc updates | pass | `node packages/cli/dist/index.js lang --cwd /tmp/pgg-shell-auto-run-and-interactive-change-exit-qa --value en` -> `status=changed`, updated includes `.codex/add/*`, `.codex/skills/*`, `AGENTS.md`, `.pgg/project.json` |\n| QA-006 | auto summary | pass | `node packages/cli/dist/index.js auto --cwd /tmp/pgg-shell-auto-run-and-interactive-change-exit-qa --value off` -> `status=changed`, updated includes `.pgg/project.json` |\n| QA-007 | PTY interactive changed path | pass | PTY `teams` Enter -> `status=changed`, updated path `.pgg/project.json` |\n| QA-008 | PTY interactive cancelled path | pass | PTY `teams` Ctrl+C -> `status=cancelled` |\n| QA-009 | trusted helper contract surface | pass | `packages/core/src/templates.ts`, `packages/core/src/readme.ts`, `README.md`, `AGENTS.md`, `.codex/add/SHELL-RULES.md`, `.codex/skills/pgg-*.md` |\n\n## Expert Notes\n\n| Expert | Score | Summary | Blocking |\n|---|---:|---|---|\n| QA/н…ҢмҠӨнҠё м—”м§ҖлӢҲм–ҙ | 99 | gate, build, sample CLI, PTY interactive кІҪлЎңлҘј лӢӨмӢң мӢӨн–үн–Ҳкі  changed/unchanged/cancelled м¶ңл Ҙмқҙ лӘЁл‘җ нҷ•мқёлҗҗлӢӨ. | м—ҶмқҢ |\n| мҪ”л“ң лҰ¬л·°м–ҙ | 97 | `.pgg/project.json`мқ„ summaryм—җ нҸ¬н•Ён•ҳлҸ„лЎқ ліҙк°•н•ң л’Ө `teams` ліҖкІҪмқҙ мӢӨм ң `changed`лЎң л“ңлҹ¬лӮҳлҠ” м җмқ„ нҷ•мқён–ҲлӢӨ. | м—ҶмқҢ |\n| SRE / мҡҙмҳҒ м—”м§ҖлӢҲм–ҙ | 98 | trusted helper лІ”мң„к°Җ generated/managed `.codex/sh/*.sh`лЎң н•ңм •лҗҳм–ҙ arbitrary shell мһҗлҸҷ мӢӨн–үмңјлЎң н•ҙм„қлҗ  м—¬м§Җк°Җ мӨ„м—Ҳкі , archive helper мӢӨн–ү м „м ң мЎ°кұҙлҸ„ м¶©мЎұлҗҗлӢӨ. | м—ҶмқҢ |\n\n## Decision\n\n- pass\n\n## Residual Risks\n\n- PTY interactive кІҖмҰқмқҖ `teams` лӘ…л №мңјлЎң мҲҳн–үн–ҲлӢӨ. `lang`кіј `auto`лҠ” к°ҷмқҖ `choose()` кІҪлЎңлҘј кіөмң н•ҳм§Җл§Ң PTYм—җм„ң к°ңлі„ мһ¬мӢӨн–үн•ҳм§ҖлҠ” м•Ҡм•ҳлӢӨ.\n- dashboard buildлҠ” м„ұкіөн–Ҳм§Җл§Ң large chunk warningмқҖ кё°мЎҙмІҳлҹј лӮЁм•„ мһҲлӢӨ. мқҙлІҲ topic лІ”мң„ л°–мқҙлӢӨ.\n",
